{"tid":1824861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實仲係咪五大訴求缺一不可","createTime":"2020-01-14T20:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T23:34:43.000Z","uid":251581,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"399423044658803df7d4ba6999cd3add30f14c77","tid":1824861,"uid":251581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T20:33:41.000Z","msg":"因為呢個係一個要求 <br />\n要求政府 中共 比你<br />\n咁既然你要革命 革命就係要推翻政府<br />\n或者走獨立既路<br />\n五大訴求係咪同革命衝突左<br />\n五大 全部都係要求政府既一個讓步<br />\n直接講雙普選 拖到2047都唔會有啦 <br />\n政府係唔會回應訴求<br />\n中共係唔會讓步<br />\n所以不停講止暴制亂 佢唔諗住比我地有民主<br />\n只係想我地停止一切所謂既暴力行為<br />\n咁 訴同求 告訴你 要求你<br />\n但中共唔聽 點告訴 中共唔讓步 點要求<br />\n不如直接 <br />\n奪回香港主權 自己自由自己爭取（9UP）"},{"pid":"1dccbd27c2566ba14d4461e2cd30e158575c66b8","tid":1824861,"uid":62841,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T20:34:49.000Z","msg":"點解你會有香港人想搞革命呢個錯覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fbe40da22dd2708c06f57b3701161160f6147a","tid":1824861,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T20:36:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7380efff07f6d5221a6998bf2ce10f53e3f47032","tid":1824861,"uid":251581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dccbd27c2566ba14d4461e2cd30e158575c66b8","tid":1824861,"uid":62841,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T20:34:49.000Z","msg":"點解你會有香港人想搞革命呢個錯覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T21:15:37.000Z","msg":"生活革命<br />\n唔需要流血 暴力<br />\n食下野就得"},{"pid":"88cc336627770d54d0778cc4f813f3ac2cc9ebec","tid":1824861,"uid":280739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T23:34:43.000Z","msg":"一步一步黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申： 承認獨立"}]}